  "ciliary_role": "Zinc-finger transcription factor that mediates transcriptio l repression via its interaction with the nucleosome- remodeling deacetylase (NuRD) complex. Truncated SALL1 interacts with or sequester factors related to cilia function, including the negative regulators of ciliogenesis CCP110 and CEP97. SALL1 mutations can disrupt cilia formation and function (29395072). Truncated SALL1 increases the ubiquitin proteasome- mediated degradation of LUZP1, contributing to Townes-Brocks Syndrome (32553112).",
